title: World News | Estonian President Hails 'ancient' Ties with India; Seeks Deeper Cooperation in AI, Green Tech
description: Get latest articles and stories on World at LatestLY. Marking the upcoming anniversary of the Republic of Estonia, President Alar Karis emphasised the deep-rooted historical parallels between Estonia and India, describing both nations as "ancient Europeans" and a "cradle of civilisation" respectively.

title: Cape Breton fossil sheds light on the first four-legged herbivore
description: This football-sized creature could grind its teeth like a hard-core plant-eater, back before that was really a thing — and it may be the earliest vertebrate herbivore ever found.
